Dear Tamar and Adam

As per our earlier discussions, I understand you would like to proceed with=
 the application for a cash backed clean capital loan, for USD 4 million.
This is to preserve your capital as clean capital, and use the proceeds of =
the loan for reinvestment purposes via your existing bank account at HSBC P=
rivate Bank in Guernsey. The indicative terms discussed are a margin cost o=
f 0.75% above the variable USD 1 month LIBOR.

In order to proceed with a credit application to our credit committee, we w=
ould need some further information as per the below overview.
Although the loan would be fully backed by cash, the regulator still sees t=
his as a loan facility which is why we ask for this.


=B7         Financial Analysis: although we already have information on fil=
e for you, we would need to discuss your current assets/liabilities and Inc=
ome/Expenditure.

=B7         Repayment: from which funds you plan to pay the interest balanc=
es

=B7         Investments: general understanding of the investments you are p=
lanning to make with proceeds of the loan

=B7         Opportunity to discuss interest rate risk and the future demise=
 of IBORs (reference rate). Please find attached further information for yo=
ur perusal.

I suggest to plan a call or a Zoom video meeting to go over the items below=
, if that is ok with you.
I am available tomorrow afternoon, or whenever works for you next week. Ple=
ase can you let me know what is suitable for you?

Finally, we would also require a 'High Net Worth Statement', to be complete=
d by an accountant.
I will send you this in a separate email.

Do not hesitate to reach out if you have any questions at this point.

Kind regards
Loicque


Lo=EFcque Windey
Relationship Manager
HSBC Private Banking | Private Banking, HSBC UK Bank plc
8 Cork Street, London W1S 3LJ, United Kingdom

T: +44 (0)20 7860 3308 | M: +44 (0)7408 830710
E-mail:loicque.windey@hsbcpb.com
Website: www.hsbcprivatebank.com<http://www.hsbcprivatebank.com/>

